#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaffeine; Player"
msgstr "&kaffeine; Predvajalnik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Start Window"
msgstr "Začetno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like many other media players, &kaffeine; supports a wide range of video and "
"audio formats as well as playing audio and video from DVD and &CD;. "
"Additionally, it supports live Digital TV playback if your machine has a "
"Digital Video Broadcast (DVB) device plugged into it."
msgstr ""
"Kot mnogi drugi medijski predvajalniki, &kaffeine; podpira široko paleto "
"video in avdio formatov ter predvajanje zvoka in videa z DVD-jev in &CD;. "
"Poleg tega podpira predvajanje digitalne televizije v živo, če ima vaša "
"naprava priključeno napravo za digitalno video oddajanje (DVB)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once &kaffeine; starts, it presents a screen with the main functions in the "
"middle, and it’s possible to switch to other functions via either the menu "
"bar or the left sidebar:"
msgstr ""
"Ko se enkrat &kaffeine; zažene, prikaže zaslon z glavnimi funkcijami na "
"sredini, na druge funkcije pa je mogoče preklopiti prek menijske vrstice ali "
"leve stranske vrstice:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Start Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Začetno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Start Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Začetno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Play a File</title>"
msgstr "<title>Predvajaj datoteko</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Playing a video or audio file is as simple as clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Play File</guibutton> button. It will ask you to select the file "
"to be played, and will begin playing it. Since &kaffeine; uses LibVLC for "
"the backend, it supports all the same <ulink url=\"https://www.videolan.org/"
"vlc/features.html\">file formats</ulink> as VLC. It also supports opening a "
"list of files to create and manage <ulink url=\"https://wiki.videolan.org/"
"Playlist/\">playlists</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Predvajanje video ali zvočne datoteke je preprosto kot klik na gumb "
"<guibutton>Predvajaj datoteko</guibutton>. Pozval vas bo, da izberete "
"datoteko za predvajanje, in jo začel predvajati. Ker &kaffeine; uporablja "
"LibVLC za zaledje, podpira vse <ulink url=\"https://www.videolan.org/vlc/"
"features.html\">formate datotek</ulink> kot VLC. Podpira tudi odpiranje "
"seznama datotek za ustvarjanje in upravljanje <ulink url=\"https://wiki."
"videolan.org/Playlist/\">seznamov predvajanja</ulink>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Play a File</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Predvajaj datoteko</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Play a File</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Predvajaj datoteko</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Playlist Window"
msgstr "Okno seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaffeine; supports multiple playlists. Choose the active one with the "
"<guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> selector in the left sidebar. You can easily "
"drag some files or folders from the file browser and drop it on the playlist "
"to enqueue or drop it on the player window to create a new playlist. To "
"change a playlist name edit it and confirm with <keycap>Return</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"&kaffeine; podpira več seznamov predvajanja. Izberite aktivnega z izbirnikom "
"<guilabel>Seznam predvajanja</guilabel> v levi stranski vrstici. Nekatere "
"datoteke ali mape lahko preprosto povlečete iz brskalnika datotek in jih "
"spustite na seznam predvajanja, da jih postavite v čakalno vrsto, ali jih "
"spustite v okno predvajalnika, da ustvarite nov seznam predvajanja. Če "
"želite spremeniti ime seznama predvajanja, ga uredite in potrdite s "
"<keycap>Return</keycap>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Playlist Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Okno seznama predvajanja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Playlist Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Okno seznama predvajanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find all playlist related functions in the <guimenu>Playlist</"
"guimenu> item from the menu bar and the context-menu (right-click on "
"playlist)."
msgstr ""
"Vse funkcije, povezane s seznamom predvajanja, najdete v elementu "
"<guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> v menijski vrstici in kontekstnem "
"meniju (z desnim klikom na seznam predvajanja)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Digital TV Player"
msgstr "Digitalni TV predvajalnik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Digital TV configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija digitalne televizije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While the basic functionality is useful enough for someone who wants a "
"simple, yet powerful media player, the best feature in &kaffeine; is to use "
"it as a &GUI; frontend to watch and record digital TV."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je osnovna funkcionalnost dovolj uporabna za nekoga, ki želi "
"preprost, a zmogljiv večpredstavnostni predvajalnik, je najboljša funkcija "
"&kaffeine; je, da ga uporabite kot &GUI; vmesnik za gledanje in snemanje "
"digitalne televizije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &kaffeine; version 2.0, the digital TV support uses libdvbv5 and was "
"extended to support new standards like DVB-T2 and ISDB-T. Extending its "
"support for newer digital TV standards is now simpler. Also, since it uses "
"the &Linux; DVB version 5 API, it supports frontends capable of implementing "
"multiple digital TV standards."
msgstr ""
"Ker &kaffeine; različici 2.0 podpora za digitalno televizijo uporablja "
"libdvbv5 in je bila razširjena na podporo novim standardom, kot sta DVB-T2 "
"in ISDB-T. Razširitev podpore za novejše standarde digitalne televizije je "
"zdaj preprostejša. Poleg tega, ker uporablja &Linux; DVB različica 5 API, "
"podpira vmesnike, ki lahko implementirajo več standardov digitalne "
"televizije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Setting the TV configuration on &kaffeine; is as simple as open the "
"<guimenu>Television</guimenu> item from the menu bar and select the "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Television...</guimenuitem> option. A pop up window "
"will open, allowing setting the parameters to be used:"
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev TV konfiguracije na &kaffeine; je tako preprosto, kot da v "
"menijski vrstici odprete element <guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> in izberete "
"možnost <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj televizijo...</guimenuitem>. Odpre se "
"pojavno okno, v katerem lahko nastavite parametre, ki jih želite uporabiti:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>TV Configuration - General Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija TV - splošne možnosti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>TV Configuration - General Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija TV - splošne možnosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "General digital TV settings"
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve digitalne televizije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>General Options</guimenu> menu allows setting the device-"
"independent settings."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Splošne možnosti</guimenu> omogoča nastavitev nastavitev, "
"neodvisnih od naprave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Recording folder</guilabel> sets the location where all TV "
"program records will be stored."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Mapa za snemanje</guilabel> nastavi lokacijo, kjer bodo shranjeni "
"vsi posnetki TV-programov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>xmltv file name (optional)</guilabel> specifies a file name "
"with EPG data that was retrieved via an external grabber. When this option "
"is used, you'll likely set <guilabel>Disable parsing Electronic Program "
"Guide (EPG) data from MPEG-TS tables</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime datoteke xmltv (neobvezno)</guilabel> podaja ime datoteke s "
"podatki EPG, ki je bila pridobljena prek zunanjega zajemalnika. Ko uporabite "
"to možnost, boste verjetno nastavili <guilabel>Onemogoči razčlenjevanje "
"podatkov elektronskega programskega vodnika (EPG) iz tabel MPEG-TS</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Disable parsing EPG data from MPEG-TS tables</guilabel> "
"disables the Electronic Program Guide (EPG) data to be retrieved from the "
"broadcasted signal. Use it in order to save some CPU time, if your "
"broadcaster doesn't send reliable EPG data."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Onemogoči razčlenjevanje podatkov EPG iz tabel MPEG-TS</guilabel> "
"onemogoči pridobivanje podatkov elektronskega programskega vodnika (EPG) iz "
"oddanega signala. Uporabite ga, da prihranite nekaj časa procesorja, če vaš "
"izdajatelj televizijskega programa ne pošilja zanesljivih podatkov EPG."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Time shift folder</guilabel> is used in conjunction with the "
"pause button (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-"
"playback-pause-circular.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>) of the media player screen. When the button is pressed, "
"a time shift file will be stored at the location pointed by this menu option."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Mapa časovni zamik</guilabel> se uporablja v povezavi z gumbom za "
"premor (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-"
"pause-circular.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>) "
"zaslona predvajalnika medijev. Ko pritisnete gumb, se datoteka s časovnim "
"zamikom shrani na mesto, ki ga kaže ta možnost  menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Begin margin</guilabel> and <guilabel>End margin</guilabel> "
"options are used to setup a sort of <quote>security margin</quote> in order "
"to avoid losing the beginning and the end of a program, as the time stamps "
"at the program guide may not be precise. So, it actually starts recording a "
"few minutes before the <guilabel>Start</guilabel> time defined in the "
"<guimenu>Program Guide</guimenu>. The exact amount of time before is defined "
"via <guilabel>Begin margin</guilabel>. &kaffeine; extends the record by the "
"amount of time defined by <guilabel>End margin</guilabel> after the end of "
"the program."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti <guilabel>Začetni rob</guilabel> in <guilabel>Končni rob</guilabel> "
"se uporabljata za nastavitev neke vrste <quote>varnostnega roba</quote>, da "
"preprečite izgubo začetka in konca programa , saj časovni žigi v programskem "
"vodniku morda niso natančni. Torej dejansko začne snemati nekaj minut pred "
"<guilabel>Začetnim</guilabel> časom, določenim v <guimenu>Programskem "
"vodniku</guimenu>. Natančen čas pred tem je določen prek <guilabel>Začetni "
"rob</guilabel>. &kaffeine; podaljša zapis za čas, ki ga definira "
"<guilabel>Končni rob</guilabel> po koncu programa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Naming style for recordings</guilabel> option is used to setup "
"how &kaffeine; will name a program. Several macros can be used to "
"dynamically change the name of the record:"
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Slog poimenovanja za posnetke</guilabel> se uporablja za "
"nastavitev načina &kaffeine; bo poimenoval program. Za dinamično "
"spreminjanje imena zapisa je mogoče uporabiti več makrov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>%title</parameter> - Title of the program, as seen at the "
"<guimenu>Program Guide</guimenu> and <guimenu>Recording Schedule</guimenu> "
"menus;"
msgstr ""
"<parameter>%title</parameter> - Naslov programa, kot ga vidite v menijih "
"<guimenu>Vodnik po programih</guimenu> in <guimenu>Urnik snemanja</guimenu>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>%day, %month, %year, %hour, %min, %sec</parameter> - Fields from "
"the time stamp with represents the time when &kaffeine; starts recording a "
"program;"
msgstr ""
"<parameter>%dan, %mesec, %leto, %ura, %min, %sek</parameter> - Polja iz "
"časovnega žiga s predstavlja čas, ko &kaffeine; začne snemati program;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>%channel</parameter> - Name of the channel that streamed the "
"program."
msgstr "<parameter>%channel</parameter> – Ime kanala, ki je pretakal program."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Action after recording finishes</guilabel> option is used to "
"setup an optional command to be executed when &kaffeine; stops recording a "
"program."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Dejanje po končanem snemanju</guilabel> se uporablja za "
"nastavitev neobveznega ukaza, ki naj se izvede, ko &kaffeine; ustavi "
"snemanje programa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking at the <guilabel>Update Scan Data over Internet</guilabel> option "
"makes &kaffeine; to check if a new channel scanning definition file is "
"present at <ulink url=\"https://autoconfig.kde.org/kaffeine/\"> KDE's site</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete možnost <guilabel>Posodobi skenirane podatke prek interneta</"
"guilabel>, &kaffeine; da preverite, ali je na <ulink url=\"https://"
"autoconfig.kde.org/kaffeine/\"> mestu KDE</ulink> prisotna nova datoteka z "
"definicijo skeniranja kanalov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaffeine; uses a file called scanfile.dvb to store a list of known digital "
"TV channels per Country and City. This file is kept in sync with the "
"contents of <ulink url=\"https://git.linuxtv.org/dtv-scan-tables.git\">the "
"dtv-scan-tables tree</ulink>, maintained by <ulink url=\"https://linuxtv.org"
"\">LinuxTV</ulink> community. For more details, please see <ulink url="
"\"https://linuxtv.org/wiki/index.php/Dtv-scan-tables\">the dtv-scan-tables "
"wiki page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kaffeine; uporablja datoteko, imenovano scanfile.dvb, za shranjevanje "
"seznama znanih digitalnih televizijskih kanalov po državah in mestih. Ta "
"datoteka je sinhronizirana z vsebino <ulink url=\"https://git.linuxtv.org/"
"dtv-scan-tables.git\">drevesa dtv-scan-tables</ulink>, ki ga vzdržuje <ulink "
"url=\"https://linuxtv.org\">skupnost LinuxTV</ulink>. Za več podrobnosti si "
"oglejte <ulink url=\"https://linuxtv.org/wiki/index.php/Dtv-scan-tables"
"\">wiki stran dtv-scan-tables</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the button is clicked, &kaffeine; will download the latest version of "
"the channel definitions and store on a user-specific local data file, "
"overriding any contents of a previous one."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb, &kaffeine; bo prenesel najnovejšo različico definicij "
"kanala in jih shranil v uporabniško specifično lokalno podatkovno datoteko, "
"pri čemer bo preglasil kakršno koli vsebino prejšnje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please notice that, in order to use the newest definitions, it is required "
"to close the TV configuration dialog and reopen."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je za uporabo najnovejših definicij potrebno zapreti "
"pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo televizorja in ga znova odpreti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Edit scanfile</guilabel> option allows editing the file, which "
"can be useful to add a new set of channels, while the upstream file is not "
"updated. If you need to use it, please consider sending an update to <ulink "
"url=\"https://git.linuxtv.org/dtv-scan-tables.git/\">dtv-scan-tables </"
"ulink> for others to also benefit from the new channel definitions."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Uredi skenirano datoteko</guilabel> omogoča urejanje "
"datoteke, kar je lahko koristno za dodajanje novega nabora kanalov, medtem "
"ko se datoteka navzgor ne posodobi. Če ga morate uporabiti, razmislite o "
"pošiljanju posodobitve na <ulink url=\"https://git.linuxtv.org/dtv-scan-"
"tables.git/\">dtv-scan-tables </ulink> za lahko tudi drugi koristijo nove "
"definicije kanalov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Use ISO 8859-1 charset instead of ISO 6937</guilabel> option "
"allows selecting the default to be used on MPEG-TS messages that don't "
"explicitly set a charset. If not set, it defaults to using ISO-6937 "
"encoding. If set, the default changes to ISO 8859-1."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Uporabi nabor znakov ISO 8859-1 namesto ISO 6937</"
"guilabel> omogoča izbiro privzete vrednosti za uporabo v sporočilih MPEG-TS, "
"ki ne določajo izrecno nabora znakov. Če ni nastavljeno, je privzeto "
"uporabljeno kodiranje ISO-6937. Če je nastavljeno, se privzeta vrednost "
"spremeni v ISO 8859-1."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Create info files to accompany EPG recordings</guilabel> "
"option enables the creation of ancillary files for scheduled records with "
"the contents of the program guide for records made via the <guimenu>Program "
"guide</guimenu>."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Ustvari informacijske datoteke za spremljanje posnetkov "
"EPG</guilabel> omogoča ustvarjanje pomožnih datotek za načrtovana snemanja z "
"vsebino programskega vodnika za zapise, narejene prek <guimenu>Programskega "
"vodnika</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Electronic Program Guide (EPG) data retrieval"
msgstr "Pridobivanje podatkov elektronskega programskega vodnika (EPG)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most digital TV broadcasters send program information via the broadcast "
"information, encoded on a MPEG-TS stream. However, some of them use non-"
"standard encodings for those data. As an example, at the United Kingdom, HD "
"programs EPG data are usually stored using some a proprietary format. Other "
"providers just don't fill the EPG data, or the information there is not "
"reliable."
msgstr ""
"Večina izdajateljev digitalnih televizijskih programov pošilja informacije o "
"programu prek informacij o oddaji, kodiranih v toku MPEG-TS. Vendar nekateri "
"od njih za te podatke uporabljajo nestandardna kodiranja. Na primer, v "
"Združenem kraljestvu so podatki EPG programov visoke ločljivosti običajno "
"shranjeni v nekem lastniškem formatu. Drugi ponudniki pač ne polnijo EPG "
"podatkov ali pa tam podatki niso zanesljivi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &kaffeine; 2.0.17, it is possible to disable parsing the EPG data from "
"the broadcasted channels, using an external program to retrieve them. In "
"order to disable, just set the <guilabel>Disable parsing Electronic Program "
"Guide (EPG) data from MPEG-TS tables</guilabel> box. You can now set an "
"external parser to produce a file with EPG data, and use the <guilabel>xmltv "
"file name (optional)</guilabel> to specify the file name of the produced "
"file. The produced file should use the XMLTV format, as described on its "
"DTD. See <ulink url=\"http://wiki.xmltv.org/index.php/XMLTVFormat\"> XMLTV "
"File format</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Od različice &kaffeine; 2.0.17 je mogoče onemogočiti razčlenjevanje podatkov "
"EPG iz predvajanih kanalov z uporabo zunanjega programa za njihovo "
"pridobitev. Če želite onemogočiti, nastavite polje <guilabel>Onemogoči "
"razčlenjevanje podatkov elektronskega programskega vodnika (EPG) iz tabel "
"MPEG-TS</guilabel>. Zdaj lahko nastavite zunanji razčlenjevalnik, da ustvari "
"datoteko s podatki EPG, in uporabite <guilabel>ime datoteke xmltv "
"(neobvezno)</guilabel>, da določite ime proizvedene datoteke. Izdelana "
"datoteka mora uporabljati format XMLTV, kot je opisano v njenem DTD. Za več "
"informacij glejte <ulink url=\"http://wiki.xmltv.org/index.php/XMLTVFormat"
"\"> Format datoteke XMLTV</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &kaffeine; is set to use an XMLTV file, it will automatically detect "
"any file changes on it. When a change happens, it will open the file and "
"parse its contents, updating EPG data accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Ko je &kaffeine; nastavljen za uporabo datoteke XMLTV, bo samodejno zaznal "
"vse spremembe datoteke v njej. Ko pride do spremembe, bo odprl datoteko in "
"razčlenil njeno vsebino ter ustrezno posodobil podatke EPG."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It should be noticed that the XMLTV file has a table with associates its own "
"internal representation for channels with the expected channel name at the "
"digital TV broadcasted data. &kaffeine; will only retrieve the EPG data if "
"the channels there match the ones inside &kaffeine;'s channel list. So, you "
"need to ensure that the channels there matches what &kaffeine; expects. If "
"it doesn't match, you could use a command line &XML; editor program in order "
"to add the missing channel information."
msgstr ""
"Treba je opozoriti, da ima datoteka XMLTV tabelo s pridruženimi lastnimi "
"notranjimi predstavitvami za kanale s pričakovanim imenom kanala pri "
"oddajanih podatkih digitalne televizije. &kaffeine; bo pridobil podatke EPG "
"samo, če se tamkajšnji kanali ujemajo s tistimi na seznamu kanalov "
"&kaffeine;. Torej morate zagotoviti, da se kanali tam ujemajo s tem, kar "
"&kaffeine; pričakuje. Če se ne ujema, lahko uporabite ukazno vrstico &XML; "
"urejevalnika, da dodate manjkajoče informacije o kanalu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if you have a xmltv grabber program retrieving the file named "
"<emphasis>original_xmltv_file.xmltv</emphasis>, you could use the "
"<emphasis>xmlstarlet</emphasis> program to add missing associations. So, if "
"you want to associate the XMLTV channel named as <emphasis>channel.foo.uk</"
"emphasis> with a channel whose &kaffeine; name is <emphasis>FOO</emphasis>, "
"you could run this small script:"
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če imate program za zajemanje xmltv, ki pridobiva datoteko z "
"imenom <emphasis>original_xmltv_file.xmltv</emphasis>, lahko uporabite "
"program <emphasis>xmlstarlet</emphasis> za dodajanje manjkajočih povezav. "
"Torej, če želite povezati kanal XMLTV z imenom <emphasis>channel.foo.uk</"
"emphasis> s kanalom, katerega &kaffeine; ime je <emphasis>FOO</emphasis>, "
"lahko zaženete ta majhen skript:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"channel=\"xmltv.channel.pt\"\n"
"name=\"DVB_CHANNEL\"\n"
"xmlstarlet ed \\\n"
"        -s \"tv/channel[@id='$channel']\" -t elem -n display-name \\\n"
"        -v \"$name\" original_xmltv_file.xmltv &gt; new_xmltv_file.xmltv\n"
"mv new_xmltv_file.xmltv /tmp/new_xmltv_file.xmltv"
msgstr ""
"channel=\"xmltv.channel.pt\"\n"
"name=\"DVB_CHANNEL\"\n"
"xmlstarlet ed \\\n"
"        -s \"tv/channel[@id='$channel']\" -t elem -n display-name \\\n"
"        -v \"$name\" original_xmltv_file.xmltv &gt; new_xmltv_file.xmltv\n"
"mv new_xmltv_file.xmltv /tmp/new_xmltv_file.xmltv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then, set &kaffeine; to use the new <emphasis>/tmp/new_xmltv_file.xmltv</"
"emphasis> file."
msgstr ""
"Nato nastavite &kaffeine; za uporabo nove datoteke <emphasis>/tmp/"
"new_xmltv_file.xmltv</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring digital TV sources"
msgstr "Konfiguracija digitalnih TV virov"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "TV Device Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija TV naprave"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "TV Configuration"
msgstr "TV konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Device</guimenu> tabs have the per-device setup. Usually "
"selecting the country and the city in the <guilabel>Source</guilabel> combo "
"box (or using one of the Autoscan sources) is enough for non-satellite "
"configurations. The same happens for devices that support multiple TV "
"standards. On those devices, you need to setup the <guilabel>Source</"
"guilabel> for each TV standard:"
msgstr ""
"Zavihki <guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> imajo nastavitev za vsako napravo. "
"Običajno za nesatelitske konfiguracije zadostuje izbira države in mesta v "
"kombiniranem polju <guilabel>Vir</guilabel> (ali uporaba enega od virov "
"samodejnega pregleda). Enako se zgodi pri napravah, ki podpirajo več "
"televizijskih standardov. Na teh napravah morate nastaviti <guilabel>Vir</"
"guilabel> za vsak TV-standard:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Channel Configuration</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija kanala</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Channel Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija kanala</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Tuner timeout</guilabel> specifies the amount of time the "
"channel scan will wait to get a signal lock. Usually, the default is enough "
"for most devices, but if the device is too slow to lock, such value can be "
"increased."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Časovna omejitev sprejemnika</guilabel> določa, koliko časa bo "
"iskanje kanalov čakalo na zaklepanje signala. Običajno je privzeta vrednost "
"dovolj za večino naprav, če pa je naprava prepočasna za zaklepanje, se lahko "
"to vrednost poveča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Name</guilabel> specifies the name associated with source that "
"will appear selecting <guimenu>Television</guimenu> item from the menubar "
"and <guimenuitem>Channels</guimenuitem> option, for settings panel."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel> določa ime, povezano z virom, ki se bo prikazalo, "
"če izberete element <guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> v menijski vrstici in "
"možnost <guimenuitem>Kanali</guimenuitem> za ploščo z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Satellite devices"
msgstr "Satelitske naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configuration for satellite devices (DVB-S, DVB-S2) are more complex, as "
"there are different satellite system arrangements that are possible. Also, "
"on satellite systems, it is usually up to the device to power up an "
"amplifier located at the satellite dish - called LNBf - via a DC voltage."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracije za satelitske naprave (DVB-S, DVB-S2) so bolj zapletene, saj "
"so možne različne ureditve satelitskega sistema. Prav tako je pri "
"satelitskih sistemih običajno odvisno od naprave, ki napaja ojačevalnik, "
"nameščen na satelitskem krožniku - imenovan LNBf - prek enosmerne napetosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also, as satellite systems use a wide bandwidth and accept signals using "
"different polarities, it is common to use a protocol - called DiSEqC - in "
"order to select a range of channels to be received."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega, ker satelitski sistemi uporabljajo široko pasovno širino in "
"sprejemajo signale z različnimi polaritetami, je običajna uporaba protokola "
"- imenovanega DiSEqC - za izbiro vrste kanalov za sprejem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step is to teach &kaffeine; about the satellite configuration via "
"the <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> combo box:"
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak je naučiti &kaffeine; o konfiguraciji satelita prek kombiniranega "
"polja <guimenu>Konfiguracija</guimenu>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Satellite device definitions</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Definicije satelitskih naprav</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Satellite device definitions</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Definicije satelitskih naprav</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following values are possible:"
msgstr "Možne so naslednje vrednosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>DiSEqC Switch</parameter> - The antenna cable is connected to a "
"DiSEqC switch or the LNBf requires DiSEqC commands to select a range of "
"channels. This is the most common setting. It allows having up to 4 "
"satellites connected at the same time, each with its own dish. For each "
"satellite, you need to set the configuration for the LNBf at the dish "
"pointing to it."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>Stikalo DiSEqC</parameter> - Antenski kabel je priključen na "
"stikalo DiSEqC ali LNBf zahteva ukaze DiSEqC za izbiro obsega kanalov. To je "
"najpogostejša nastavitev. Omogoča povezavo do 4 satelitov hkrati, vsak s "
"svojo anteno. Za vsak satelit morate nastaviti konfiguracijo za LNBf na "
"krožniku, ki kaže nanj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>USALS Rotor</parameter> - The antenna cable is connected to a "
"single dish with a USALS Rotor, controlled via DiSEqC. Multiple satellites "
"can be configured, as the rotor will change the dish position when a "
"different satellite is chosen. You need to specify the position of the dish "
"(latitude, longitude)."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>USALS rotor</parameter> – Antenski kabel je povezan z enim "
"krožnikom z USALS rotorjem, nadzorovanim prek DiSEqC. Konfigurirate lahko "
"več satelitov, saj bo rotor spremenil položaj krožnika, ko izberete drug "
"satelit. Določiti morate položaj krožnika (geografska širina, dolžina)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>Positions Rotor</parameter> - The antenna cable is connected to a "
"single dish with a Rotor with a set of fixed positions, controlled via "
"DiSEqC. Multiple satellites can be configured, as the rotor will change the "
"dish position when a different satellite is chosen."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>Pozicijski rotor</parameter> – Antenski kabel je povezan z enim "
"krožnikom z rotorjem z naborom fiksnih položajev, nadzorovanih prek DiSEqC. "
"Konfigurirate lahko več satelitov, saj bo rotor spremenil položaj krožnika, "
"ko izberete drug satelit."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>Disable DiSEqC</parameter> - The antenna cable is connected to a "
"dish without any elements supporting DiSEqC. This setup is typically used "
"with multipoint bandstacked LNBf, where all channels are present at the same "
"time at the antenna cabling."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>Onemogoči DiSEqC</parameter> - Antenski kabel je priključen na "
"krožnik brez elementov, ki podpirajo DiSEqC. Ta nastavitev se običajno "
"uporablja pri LNBf z večtočkovnim pasovnim skladom, kjer so vsi kanali "
"prisotni hkrati na antenskem kablu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On a typical satellite system, the LNBf uses the power up voltage to select "
"between a lower voltage (13V) for vertical or circular right polarization "
"and a higher voltage (18V) for horizontal or circular left polarization. "
"However, due to cabling loss, sometimes the LNBf doesn't understand the high "
"voltage and several channels won't tune or will tune wrong. So, a few "
"devices offer an option to increase the voltage to a higher setting (14V or "
"19V). This is enabled via the tri-state <guilabel>Use Higher LNBf voltage</"
"guilabel> option. Three values are possible:"
msgstr ""
"V tipičnem satelitskem sistemu LNBf uporablja vklopno napetost za izbiro med "
"nižjo napetostjo (13 V) za navpično ali krožno desno polarizacijo in višjo "
"napetostjo (18 V) za vodoravno ali krožno levo polarizacijo. Vendar pa "
"zaradi izgube kablov LNBf včasih ne razume visoke napetosti in več kanalov "
"se ne uglasi ali pa se uglasi napačno. Tako nekaj naprav ponuja možnost "
"povečanja napetosti na višjo nastavitev (14 V ali 19 V). To je omogočeno z "
"možnostjo <guilabel>Uporabi višjo napetost LNBf</guilabel> s tremi stanji. "
"Možne so tri vrednosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>tri-state</parameter> - Don't send a command to the device to "
"adjust the voltage level. That's the default."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>tri-state</parameter> – Ne pošljite ukaza napravi za prilagoditev "
"ravni napetosti. To je privzeto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>unselected</parameter> - Use normal values (13V/18V) for the DC "
"voltage. Only select it if the device supports adjusting the level."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>unselected</parameter> - Uporabite normalne vrednosti (13V/18V) "
"za enosmerno napetost. Izberite le, če naprava podpira prilagajanje nivoja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<parameter>selected</parameter> - Use higher values (14V/19V) for the DC "
"voltage. Only select it if the device supports adjusting the level."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>selected</parameter> - Uporabite višje vrednosti (14V/19V) za "
"enosmerno napetost. Izberite le, če naprava podpira prilagajanje nivoja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configurations without a rotor"
msgstr "Konfiguracije brez rotorja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When either <parameter>DiSEqC Switch</parameter> or <parameter>Disable "
"DiSEqC </parameter> options are used, the first step is to set the satellite "
"that will be used as a signal source, via a combo box on the right. With a "
"DiSEqC switch, it is possible to select up to 4 sources. Each with its own "
"LNBf. After setting the source(s), for each source, click at the "
"corresponding <guilabel>LNBf Settings</guilabel> button to open a popup "
"window to select the LNBf type inside the dish that corresponds to the "
"source:"
msgstr ""
"Ko sta uporabljeni možnosti <parameter>DiSEqC Switch</parameter> ali "
"<parameter>Disable DiSEqC</parameter>, je prvi korak nastavitev satelita, ki "
"bo uporabljen kot vir signala, prek kombiniranega polja na desni. S stikalom "
"DiSEqC je mogoče izbrati do 4 vire. Vsak s svojim LNBf. Ko nastavite vir(e), "
"za vsak vir kliknite ustrezni gumb <guilabel>Nastavitve LNBf</guilabel>, da "
"odprete pojavno okno za izbiro vrste LNBf znotraj krožnika, ki ustreza viru:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>LNBf definitions</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Definicije LNBf</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>LNBf definitions</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Definicije LNBf</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotor configurations"
msgstr "Konfiguracije rotorja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a rotor is used, there is just one LNBf which is shared with multiple "
"satellites. So, the next step is to select the LNBf type via the "
"<guilabel>LNB Settings</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko se uporablja rotor, obstaja samo en LNBf, ki je v skupni rabi z več "
"sateliti. Torej, naslednji korak je izbira vrste LNBf v pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Nastavitve LNB</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For USALS rotor, the positioning is done via satellite position (latitude, "
"longitude). So, just select the satellites that will be used via a combo box "
"and click at the <guilabel>Add Satellite</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Pri rotorju USALS se pozicioniranje izvede preko satelitske pozicije "
"(zemljepisna širina, dolžina). Torej preprosto izberite satelite, ki jih "
"boste uporabili prek kombiniranega polja in kliknite na gumb <guilabel>Dodaj "
"satelit</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For positions rotor, the positioning is done via a preconfigured position "
"number. So, just select the satellite position at the number dialog on the "
"left and the satellite via a combo box on the right and click at the "
"<guilabel>Add Satellite</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Pri pozicijskem rotorju se pozicioniranje izvede prek vnaprej konfigurirane "
"številke položaja. Torej samo izberite položaj satelita v pogovornem oknu s "
"številkami na levi in satelit prek kombiniranega polja na desni ter kliknite "
"gumb <guilabel>Dodaj satelit</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a satellite was added by mistake, you can select the satellite and click "
"at the <guilabel>Remove Satellite</guilabel> button to remove it."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil satelit dodan pomotoma, ga lahko izberete in kliknete gumb "
"<guilabel>Odstrani satelit</guilabel>, da ga odstranite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Digital TV channel setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev digitalnega TV kanala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After clicking on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button, the next step is to "
"scan for the digital channels, using the <guimenu>Television</guimenu> item "
"from the menubar and select <guimenuitem>Channels</guimenuitem> option, for "
"settings panel:"
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> je naslednji korak iskanje "
"digitalnih kanalov z uporabo elementa <guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> v "
"menijski vrstici in izbiro možnosti <guimenuitem>Kanali</guimenuitem> , za "
"ploščo z nastavitvami:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Scanning Channels</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Iskanje kanalov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scanning Channels</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skeniranje kanalov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If more then one standard is supported, the <guilabel>Source</guilabel> "
"combo box will allow you to select the one that will be used to scan. Don't "
"forget to connect the device's antenna cable to match the standard that will "
"be used."
msgstr ""
"Če je podprt več kot en standard, vam bo kombinirano polje <guilabel>Vir</"
"guilabel> omogočilo, da izberete tistega, ki bo uporabljen za skeniranje. Ne "
"pozabite priključiti antenskega kabla naprave, da bo ustrezal standardu, ki "
"bo uporabljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &kaffeine; identifies a channel, it reads a <acronym>MPEG-TS</acronym> "
"table called Network Information Table (<acronym>NIT</acronym>), which "
"contains information about channels using different tuning parameters "
"transmitted by the same broadcaster. On certain networks, it is possible "
"that some tuning parameters to be stored on several <acronym>NIT</acronym> "
"tables (called <quote>other NITs</quote>). This is more common on some cable "
"and satellite systems. By selecting <guilabel>Search transponders for other "
"Networks</guilabel>, &kaffeine; is instructed to wait and parse all other "
"<acronym>NITs</acronym>, which may make it to find more channels, at the "
"cost of taking a lot more time to complete the channel scan operation."
msgstr ""
"Ko &kaffeine; identificira kanal, prebere tabelo <acronym>MPEG-TS</acronym>, "
"imenovano Tabela omrežnih informacij (<acronym>NIT</acronym>), ki vsebuje "
"informacije o kanalih, ki uporabljajo različne nastavitvene parametre, ki "
"jih prenaša isti izdajatelj. V nekaterih omrežjih je možno, da se nekateri "
"nastavitveni parametri shranijo v več tabel <acronym>NIT</acronym> "
"(imenovanih <quote>drugi NIT</quote>). To je pogostejše pri nekaterih "
"kabelskih in satelitskih sistemih. Z izbiro <guilabel>Poišči transponderje "
"za druga omrežja</guilabel>, &kaffeine; je naročeno, naj počaka in razčleni "
"vse druge <acronym>NIT</acronym>, zaradi česar lahko najde več kanalov, za "
"ceno, da bo trajalo veliko več časa za dokončanje operacije skeniranja "
"kanalov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The channel scan operation is started by clicking on <guibutton>Start Scan</"
"guibutton>. Once finished, the discovered channels will appear on the right. "
"These channels can be copied to the left side by clicking <guibutton>Add "
"Filtered</guibutton>. It is possible to check the tuning parameters for the "
"channel in the left side by clicking on the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> "
"button. Some parameters are adjustable in the window that pops up."
msgstr ""
"Operacijo skeniranja kanalov zaženete s klikom na <guibutton>Začni iskanje</"
"guibutton>. Ko končate, se odkriti kanali prikažejo na desni. Te kanale "
"lahko kopirate na levo stran s klikom na <guibutton>Dodaj filtrirano</"
"guibutton>. Nastavitvene parametre za kanal na levi strani lahko preverite s "
"klikom na gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>. Nekatere parametre je mogoče "
"nastaviti v oknu, ki se odpre."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Edit Channel Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urejanje nastavitev kanala</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Edit Channel Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urejanje nastavitev kanala</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the channels are saved, watching TV is as simple as clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Digital TV</guibutton> button in the main window:"
msgstr ""
"Ko so kanali shranjeni, je gledanje televizije preprosto kot klik na gumb "
"<guibutton>Digitalna TV</guibutton> v glavnem oknu:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Watching TV</title>"
msgstr "<title>Gledanje televizije</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Watching TV</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gledanje televizije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Watching TV</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gledanje televizije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaffeine; also allows you to click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-pause-"
"circular.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button to "
"pause it. With this action, &kaffeine; will record the program and once the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-start-"
"circular.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button is "
"pressed it will start the program from the point it was paused, this is "
"known as time shifting. There is also a "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-save.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button that allows you to "
"quick record and save the program to disk."
msgstr ""
"&kaffeine; omogoča tudi, da kliknete gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-pause-"
"circular.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, da ga "
"začasno ustavite. S tem dejanjem &kaffeine; bo posnel program in ko bo "
"pritisnjen gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-"
"playback-start-circular.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>, bo začel program od točke, ko je bil začasno ustavljen, "
"je to znano kot časovni premik. Obstaja tudi gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-save.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, ki omogoča hitro "
"snemanje in shranjevanje programa na disk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Program Guide</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vodnik po programu</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Digital TV channels usually transmit a list of the current and future "
"attractions. This is called Electronic Program Guide - <acronym>EPG</"
"acronym>. The EPG data is captured when a channel's content is played. To "
"see the <acronym>EPG</acronym>, open the <guimenu>Television</guimenu> item "
"from the menubar and select the <guimenuitem>Program Guide</guimenuitem> "
"option:"
msgstr ""
"Digitalni televizijski kanali običajno prenašajo seznam trenutnih in "
"prihodnjih zanimivosti. To se imenuje elektronski programski vodnik - "
"<acronym>EPG</acronym>. Podatki EPG se zajamejo, ko se predvaja vsebina "
"kanala. Za ogled <acronym>EPG</acronym> odprite element <guimenu>Televizija</"
"guimenu> v menijski vrstici in izberite možnost <guimenuitem>Programski "
"vodnik</guimenuitem>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Program Guide</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Programski vodnik</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Program Guide</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Programski vodnik</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On some Countries, the EPG may be available in multiple languages. By "
"default, &kaffeine; shows any languages on EPG. If multiple languages are "
"available for a given EPG entry, and no explicit language content is select, "
"it will prefix the title, subtitle and description data with a 3 letter "
"language code, as defined by ISO 639-2 specification."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih državah je lahko EPG na voljo v več jezikih. Privzeto je, da "
"&kaffeine; prikazuje vse jezike v EPG. Če je za dani vnos EPG na voljo več "
"jezikov in ni izbrana nobena eksplicitna jezikovna vsebina, bo naslovu, "
"podnapisom in opisnim podatkom dodal 3-črkovno kodo jezika, kot je "
"opredeljeno v specifikaciji ISO 639-2."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>EPG Language</guilabel> option allows filtering just one "
"language. If enabled, the filter will also be applied to the On Screen "
"Display - <acronym>OSD</acronym> and to any new scheduled recordings. It "
"won't affect pre-existing scheduled recordings."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Jezik EPG</guilabel> omogoča filtriranje samo enega "
"jezika. Če je omogočen, bo filter uporabljen tudi za prikaz na zaslonu - "
"<acronym>OSD</acronym> in za vse nove načrtovane posnetke. To ne bo vplivalo "
"na že obstoječe načrtovane posnetke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides clicking on the record button "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-save.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> when the live view is "
"opened, &kaffeine; also allows recording a program via the program guide, by "
"clicking on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-"
"record.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guibutton>Record Show</guibutton> at the <guimenuitem>Program Guide</"
"guimenuitem> window."
msgstr ""
"Poleg klika na gumb za snemanje <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-save.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>, ko je odprt pogled v živo, &kaffeine; omogoča tudi "
"snemanje programa prek programskega vodnika, s klikom na "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-record.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>Snemaj Pokaži</"
"guibutton> v oknu <guimenuitem>Programski vodnik</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Recording Schedule</title>"
msgstr "<title>Urnik snemanja</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see the programs that are scheduled to be recorded, open the "
"<guimenu>Television</guimenu> item from the menubar and select the "
"<guimenuitem>Recording Schedule</guimenuitem> option:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti programe, ki so načrtovani za snemanje, odprite element "
"<guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> v menijski vrstici in izberite možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Urnik snemanja</guimenuitem>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Recording Schedule</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urnik snemanja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Recording Schedule</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urnik snemanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking one the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button, it is possible to "
"directly define a time and duration for a program to be recorded. In this "
"case, it won't use the EPG definitions."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Novo</guibutton> lahko neposredno določite čas "
"in trajanje programa, ki naj se posname. V tem primeru ne bo uporabil "
"definicij EPG."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By selecting an existing program and clicking on the <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> button, you may change the start time and the record duration. "
"You may also program it to be recorded weekly or daily."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete obstoječi program in kliknete gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>, "
"lahko spremenite začetni čas in trajanje zapisa. Programirate ga lahko tudi "
"za tedensko ali dnevno snemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By selecting an existing program and clicking on the <guibutton>Remove</"
"guibutton> button, it will remove the program from the recording schedule."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete obstoječi program in kliknete gumb <guibutton>Odstrani</"
"guibutton>, bo program odstranjen iz razporeda snemanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kaffeine; menubar"
msgstr "&kaffeine; menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens the file dialog</action> and allows you to select a local file "
"to play."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre pogovorno okno datoteke</action> in vam omogoča, da izberete "
"lokalno datoteko za predvajanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open URL...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri URL...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open a dialog for text input</action>, so you can enter the &URL; of "
"a supported external media stream."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpri pogovorno okno za vnos besedila</action>, tako da lahko "
"vnesete &URL; podprtega toka zunanjega medija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:805
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Recent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri nedavno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a drop-down list to open a local recent resource</action>. It "
"has an <guimenuitem>Clear List</guimenuitem> option to clear that list."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponuja spustni seznam za odpiranje nedavnega lokalnega vira</"
"action>. Ima možnost <guimenuitem>Počisti seznam</guimenuitem> za brisanje "
"tega seznama."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Audio &CD;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj zvok &CD;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Select the playback of an Audio &CD;</action> that should already be "
"in the reading drive."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izberite predvajanje zvočnega &CD;ja</action>, ki bi že moral biti v "
"bralnem pogonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:825
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Video &CD;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj video &CD;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Select the playback of a Video &CD;</action> that should already be "
"in the reading drive."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izberite predvajanje videa &CD;</action>, ki bi že moral biti v "
"bralnem pogonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play &DVD;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj &DVD;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Select the playback of a &DVD;</action> that should already be in "
"the reading drive."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izberite predvajanje &DVD;</action>, ki bi že moral biti v bralnem "
"pogonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:845
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play &DVD; Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj &DVD; Mapa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens the file dialog</action> and allows you to select a &DVD; "
"folder to play. This folder contains the raw data found on the &DVD;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre pogovorno okno datoteke</action> in vam omogoča, da izberete "
"&DVD; mapo za predvajanje. Ta mapa vsebuje neobdelane podatke, ki jih "
"najdete na &DVD;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kaffeine;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kaffeine;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Playback Menu"
msgstr "Meni za predvajanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnji</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you playback two streams or more in one session, <action>will select the "
"previous one</action>."
msgstr ""
"Če predvajate dva toka ali več v eni seji, bo <action>izbral prejšnjega</"
"action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play/Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj/premor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-"
"pause.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icons. "
"<action>With a check box for play a stream or pause</action> what you are "
"watching. On a television's stream will proceed to record it, this is known "
"as <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_shifting\">time shifting</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"in <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-pause."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. <action>S "
"potrditvenim poljem za predvajanje toka ali premor</action>, kar gledate. "
"Tok na televiziji bo nadaljeval s snemanjem, to je znano kot <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_shifting\">časovni premik</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Backspace;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Backspace;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Stop a stream</action> what you are watching."
msgstr "<action>Ustavite tok</action> kar gledate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you playback two streams or more in one session and you are watching the "
"previous one, <action>will select the next one</action>."
msgstr ""
"Če predvajate dva toka ali več v eni seji in gledate prejšnjega, bo "
"<action>izbral naslednjega</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen Mode/Exit "
"Full Screen Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Celozaslonski način/"
"Izhod iz celozaslonskega načina</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-restore.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icons. <action>Switch the "
"full screen mode</action>."
msgstr ""
"in <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-restore.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. <action>Preklop na "
"celozaslonski način</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Minimal Mode/Exit Minimal "
"Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Minimalni način/Izhod "
"iz minimalnega načina</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-fullscreen.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icons. <action>Switch "
"the minimal mode</action>. A &GUI; mode in a window, where we only have "
"contextual menu and keyboard shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"in <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-fullscreen.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. <action>Preklop "
"minimalnega načina</action>. &GUI; način v oknu, kjer imamo samo kontekstni "
"meni in bližnjice na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Subtitle</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Podnapisi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Offers a drop-down list with <action>options related to the subtitle "
"stream(s)</action>."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja spustni seznam z <action>možnostmi, povezanimi s tokovi podnapisov</"
"action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:965
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Subtitle</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>off/<replaceable>Name-of-subtitle</replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Podnapis</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>izklopljeno/<replaceable>Ime-podnapisa</replaceable></"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Select the available subtitle</action> from this drop-down list. "
"These subtitles channels will vary depending on the content of the source "
"stream."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izberite razpoložljive podnapise</action> s tega spustnega seznama. "
"Ti kanali s podnapisi se razlikujejo glede na vsebino izvornega toka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Subtitle</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Add subtitle file</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Podnapisi</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dodaj datoteko s podnapisi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is for <action>add a local subtitle file</action> through a file "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je za <action>dodajanje lokalne datoteke s podnapisi</action> "
"prek pogovornega okna datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Audio</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zvok</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Offers a drop-down list with <action>options related to the audio stream(s)</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja spustni seznam z <action>možnostmi, povezanimi z zvočnimi tokovi</"
"action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Audio</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Audio Device</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zvok</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zvočna naprava</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Offers a drop-down list shows the <action>available audio devices</action>. "
"Only available if more than one audio device was detected when Kaffeine was "
"started."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja spustni seznam, ki prikazuje <action>razpoložljive zvočne naprave</"
"action>. Na voljo samo, če je bila ob zagonu Kaffeine zaznana več kot ena "
"zvočna naprava."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Audio</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Increase Volume</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zvok</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Povečanje glasnosti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Raise the audio volume. The volume can also be raised by positioning the "
"mouse over the media player region and scrolling the mouse wheel up."
msgstr ""
"Povečajte glasnost zvoka. Glasnost lahko povečate tudi tako, da postavite "
"miško na območje predvajalnika in pomaknete miškino kolesce navzgor."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Audio</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Decrease Volume</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zvok</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zmanjšaj glasnost</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lower the audio volume. The volume can also be decreased by positioning the "
"mouse over the media player region and scrolling the mouse wheel down."
msgstr ""
"Zmanjšajte glasnost zvoka. Glasnost lahko zmanjšate tudi tako, da postavite "
"miško na območje predvajalnika in pomaknete miškino kolesce navzdol."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Audio</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Mute "
"Volume</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zvok</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izklop zvoka</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1045
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"audio-volume-muted."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icons. Silence the "
"audio volume and return it."
msgstr ""
"in <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"audio-volume-muted."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. Utišajte glasnost "
"zvoka in jo vrnite."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Video</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Video</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Offers a drop-down list with <action>options related to the video stream(s)</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja spustni seznam z <action>možnostmi, povezanimi z videotokom(vi)</"
"action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Video</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Deinterlace</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Video</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Odstrani prepletanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Offers a drop-down list with available de-interlacing algorithms. <action>Is "
"the process of converting interlaced video</action>, such as common analog "
"television signals and more. See <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Deinterlacing\">Wikipedia</ulink> article for more details."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja spustni seznam z razpoložljivimi algoritmi za de-prepletanje. "
"<action>Je postopek pretvorbe prepletenega videa</action>, kot so običajni "
"analogni televizijski signali in drugo. Za več podrobnosti si oglejte članek "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deinterlacing\">Wikipedia</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Video</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Aspect Ratio</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Video</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razmerje stranic</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a drop-down list with available aspect ratios</action>, more "
"an <guimenuitem>Automatic</guimenuitem> option. The <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Aspect_ratio_(image)\">aspect ratio of an image</ulink> "
"describes the proportional relationship between its width and height."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponuja spustni seznam z razpoložljivimi razmerji stranic</action>, "
"bolj možnost <guimenuitem>Samodejno</guimenuitem>. <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Aspect_ratio_(image)\">Razmerje stranic slike</ulink> "
"opisuje sorazmerno razmerje med njeno širino in višino."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Video</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Video size</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Video</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Velikost videa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a drop-down list with available video sizes</action>. Change "
"the size of the image by a percentage, more <guimenuitem>Automatic</"
"guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Original Size</guimenuitem> options."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponuja spustni seznam z razpoložljivimi velikostmi videoposnetkov</"
"action>. Spremenite velikost slike za odstotek, več možnosti "
"<guimenuitem>Samodejno</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Izvirna velikost</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Jump to Position</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skoči na položaj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a spin box for setting the desired time point to which you "
"want to go</action>; with hours, minutes and seconds."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponuja vrtljivo polje za nastavitev želene časovne točke, do katere "
"želite iti</action>; z urami, minutami in sekundami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skip</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preskoči</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a drop-down list with four predefined jump times</action>. "
"With the following options:"
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponuja spustni seznam s štirimi vnaprej določenimi časi skoka</"
"action>. Z naslednjimi možnostmi:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skip</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Skip "
"60s Backward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preskoči</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preskoči 60 s nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1135
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>It goes 60 seconds back</action>."
msgstr "<action>Pomakne se 60 sekund nazaj</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skip</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Skip "
"15s Backward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preskoči</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preskoči 15 s nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>It goes 15 seconds back</action>."
msgstr "<action>Pomakne se 15 sekund nazaj</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skip</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Skip "
"15s Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preskoči</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preskoči 15 s naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>It goes 15 seconds forward</action>."
msgstr "<action>Gre za 15 sekund naprej</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skip</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Skip "
"60s Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preskoči</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preskoči 60 s naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>It goes 60 seconds forward</action>."
msgstr "<action>Gre za 60 sekund naprej</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>DVD Menu</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Meni DVD</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Start with the original &DVD; graphic menu</action>. That is "
"explored using the cursor keys and the mouse. See <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/DVD-Video\">Wikipedia</ulink> article for more details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Začnite z izvirnim &DVD; grafični meni</action>. To se raziskuje s "
"smernimi tipkami in miško. Za več podrobnosti si oglejte članek <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DVD-Video\">Wikipedia</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Title</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>The &DVD; content is divided into titles to easy navigation</"
"action>. From here you can go directly."
msgstr ""
"<action>&DVD; vsebina je razdeljena na naslove za enostavno navigacijo</"
"action>. Od tu lahko greste neposredno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Chapter</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poglavje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>The &DVD; content is divided into chapters to easy navigation</"
"action>. From here you can go directly."
msgstr ""
"<action>&DVD; vsebina je razdeljena na poglavja za enostavno navigacijo</"
"action>. Od tu lahko greste neposredno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1216
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Angle</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kot</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>A variant of the chapters: it is possible that they have included "
"several versions</action> (called <quote>angles</quote>) of certain scenes. "
"From here you can go directly."
msgstr ""
"<action>Različica poglavij: možno je, da so vključevala več različic</"
"action> (imenovanih <quote>koti</quote>) določenih prizorov. Od tu lahko "
"greste neposredno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1229
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Playlist Menu"
msgstr "Meni seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Repeat</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A check box to <action>replay in a loop the file(s)</action> that are in the "
"playlist."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje za <action>ponovno predvajanje datotek v zanki</action>, "
"ki so na seznamu predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Random</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naključno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A check box to <action>replay randomly the files</action> that are in the "
"playlist until all of them have been played."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje za <action>ponovno naključno predvajanje datotek</action>, "
"ki so na seznamu predvajanja, dokler niso vse predvajane."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1254
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Počisti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Erase all entries in the playlist</action>."
msgstr "<action>Izbriši vse vnose na seznamu predvajanja</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Create a new playlist</action>."
msgstr "<action>Ustvarite nov seznam predvajanja</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenuj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Rename the current playlist</action>."
msgstr "<action>Preimenuje trenutni seznam predvajanja</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Remove</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odstrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Remove the current playlist</action>."
msgstr "<action>Odstrani trenutni seznam predvajanja</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Save the current playlist</action>."
msgstr "<action>Shrani trenutni seznam predvajanja</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Playlist</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Seznam predvajanja</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Save the current playlist with a new name</action>."
msgstr "<action>Shrani trenutni seznam predvajanja z novim imenom</action>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Television Menu"
msgstr "Televizijski meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Television</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Channels</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kanali</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A settings panel will appear for <action>set the channels</action> "
"corresponding to your area. See <link linkend=\"dtv-channel-setup\">Digital "
"TV channel setup</link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Prikazala se bo plošča z nastavitvami za <action>nastavitev kanalov</"
"action>, ki ustrezajo vašemu območju. Za več podrobnosti si oglejte razdelek "
"<link linkend=\"dtv-channel-setup\">Nastavitev digitalnega televizijskega "
"kanala</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Television</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Program Guide</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vodnik po programih</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A window will appear for <action>manage the program guide</action>. See "
"<link linkend=\"program-guide\">Program Guide</link> section for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Pojavilo se bo okno za <action>upravljanje programskega vodnika</action>. Za "
"več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"program-guide\">Vodnik po "
"programih</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Television</guimenu> <guimenuitem>OSD</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>OSD</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show the on screen display infobox on the playback window during "
"three seconds</action> with program guide information on the current and "
"next program. Double-clicking on it to see extended information about the "
"current program, and then click again to remove this infobox. See <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/On-screen_display\">Wikipedia</ulink> "
"article for more details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži informacijsko polje na zaslonu v oknu za predvajanje za tri "
"sekunde</action> z informacijami programskega vodnika o trenutnem in "
"naslednjem programu. Dvokliknite nanj, da si ogledate razširjene informacije "
"o trenutnem programu, in nato znova kliknite, da odstranite to informacijsko "
"polje. Za več podrobnosti glejte <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"On-screen_display\">članek v Wikipediji</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Television</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Recording Schedule</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Urnik snemanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A window will appear for <action>manage the recording(s) scheduled</action>. "
"See <link linkend=\"recording-schedule\">Recording Schedule</link> section "
"for more details."
msgstr ""
"Pojavilo se bo okno za <action>upravljanje načrtovanih posnetkov</action>. "
"Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"recording-schedule"
"\">Urnik snemanja</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1380
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Television</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Instant Record</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Takojšnji zapis</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With a check box to verify your selection. <action>Start instantly recording "
"of the stream that is being played</action>."
msgstr ""
"S potrditvenim poljem za potrditev izbire. <action>Takojšnji začetek "
"snemanja toka, ki se predvaja</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Television</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Television...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Televizija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj televizijo...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A window will appear for <action>setting the parameters that manage the DVB "
"device(s)</action>. See <link linkend=\"digital-tv\">Digital TV "
"configuration</link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Pojavilo se bo okno za <action>nastavitev parametrov, ki upravljajo naprave "
"DVB</action>. Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"digital-tv"
"\">Konfiguracija digitalne televizije</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1403
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to simplify the use of the &kaffeine;, this menu only contains two "
"menu items:"
msgstr ""
"Da bi poenostavili uporabo &kaffeine;, ta meni vsebuje samo dva elementa "
"menija:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to enable, disable, and modify keyboard shortcuts. For more "
"information, see the section called <quote>Using and Customizing Shortcuts</"
"quote>."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča omogočanje, onemogočanje in spreminjanje bližnjic na tipkovnici. Za "
"več informacij si oglejte razdelek <quote>Uporaba in prilagajanje bližnjic</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kaffeine;...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kaffeine;...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the configuration panel."
msgstr "Odpre konfiguracijsko ploščo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1435
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaffeine; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more "
"information read the sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&kaffeine; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več "
"informacij preberite razdelke o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; Osnove."

